{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>資深藝人施明上月病逝，今日（23日）將於大圍寶福紀念館設靈。李家鼎與李泳豪夫婦一起到達靈堂，不過李泳豪老婆Agnes卻被拒絕入靈堂內。Agnes在靈堂外等候大約半小時，其後在靈堂外向奶奶鞠躬，然後便離開，一路沒有回答傳媒問題，由身旁的人代答。離場的時候，由黃霑女兒、施明表妹黃宇詩護送離場。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123667053040111616548093.jpeg/EvjNsQaw2-atKM3gHjvg4KeMPOz_3J9Ih8Z1dLHGdXQ\" alt=\"黃宇詩一直陪伴Agnes（陳順禎攝）\"><figcaption>黃宇詩一直陪伴Agnes（陳順禎攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123667049961361408032418.jpeg/HHSnJRzB4sE5KuYz1kvtmSlP9tOuWlFQlrZl5aC2ZeU\" alt=\"黃宇詩護送Agnes離開。（陳順禎攝）\"><figcaption>黃宇詩護送Agnes離開。（陳順禎攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260422/1123667046643535872250639.jpeg/i-fmXLBqacPyeV8uaSzEFW-lbVoPVhThOsCmHwzAph8\" alt=\"黃宇詩護送Agnes離開。（陳順禎攝）\"><figcaption>黃宇詩護送Agnes離開。（陳順禎攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T10:28:50.214553+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":204,"images":3,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}